WEBVTT

00:02.080 --> 00:04.651
"Since Lot was afraid to stay in Zoar...

00:04.840 --> 00:07.810
...he and his two daughters
settled in the hill country...

00:08.000 --> 00:10.048
...where he lived in a cave.

00:10.280 --> 00:12.851
The firstborn said to the younger:

00:13.040 --> 00:17.284
'Our father is getting old
and there is not a man in the land...

00:17.480 --> 00:22.361
...to have intercourse with us
as is the custom everywhere.

00:22.560 --> 00:28.363
Come. Let us ply our father with wine
and then lie with him...

00:28.560 --> 00:33.327
...that we may ensure
posterity by our father.'

00:33.520 --> 00:37.081
So that night,
they plied their father with wine.

00:38.480 --> 00:41.882
And the firstborn went in
and lay with her father.

00:42.080 --> 00:44.845
The next day,
the firstborn said to the younger:

00:45.040 --> 00:50.206
'Let us ply him
with wine again tonight.

00:50.440 --> 00:55.128
And then you go in and lie with him.'

00:55.360 --> 01:00.685
So that night too,
they plied their father with wine.

01:00.880 --> 01:06.762
And then the younger one went in
and lay with her father.

01:07.000 --> 01:13.281
And so it was that the two daughters
of Lot became pregnant by their father."

01:13.480 --> 01:18.884
And thus, Lord,
we maketh your word our command!

01:19.080 --> 01:20.286
Amen!

